WEBVTT

00:07.560 --> 00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:38.960 --> 01:41.880
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:48.360 --> 01:50.960
I haven't congratulated
you yet, Grand Mentor.

01:51.640 --> 01:52.800
Come on, Wangyou.

01:52.880 --> 01:53.520
‎WANGYOU

01:53.600 --> 01:56.080
Since when did you learn to tease people?

01:56.600 --> 01:58.160
I feel happy for you.

01:58.720 --> 02:01.240
After all these years,
you've finally made it.

02:02.320 --> 02:04.880
But anyway, are you not worried?

02:05.640 --> 02:06.680
Chu Zhao…

02:07.600 --> 02:10.199
What do you know about her
that makes you help her?

02:10.280 --> 02:12.560
You even abandon
the alliance with Xiao Xun.

02:13.400 --> 02:15.440
I'm not helping Chu Zhao.

02:15.520 --> 02:16.360
I'm securing

02:17.120 --> 02:19.080
my own bright future.

02:19.160 --> 02:21.800
Be careful. It may backfire.

02:22.480 --> 02:24.800
The easier a game seems,

02:24.880 --> 02:26.560
the more hidden threats there are.

02:27.160 --> 02:29.600
We learned this when we were young.

02:29.680 --> 02:30.680
It won't.

02:32.200 --> 02:33.640
Because I always have a way out.

02:35.120 --> 02:37.680
She knew Xiao Xun
would poison the young emperor.

02:38.480 --> 02:41.880
In that case, she still used him as bait

02:43.040 --> 02:44.040
just to get rid of Xiao Xun.

02:45.480 --> 02:47.280
That was a risky move.

02:47.360 --> 02:49.840
Fight to survive, fight to win.

02:49.920 --> 02:51.920
I don't care who the Emperor is.

02:53.040 --> 02:54.760
As long as I retain

02:57.040 --> 02:58.120
my high standing.

03:01.800 --> 03:02.800
I lost.

03:03.720 --> 03:05.120
Mr. Deng, Old Madam invited you to dine.

03:18.520 --> 03:19.360
I got it.

03:35.520 --> 03:36.800
I'm sorry.

03:38.800 --> 03:40.360
I shouldn't have used you as bait.

03:42.120 --> 03:45.040
I swore to the late emperor
I'd keep you safe.

03:47.080 --> 03:49.160
But I put you in danger.

03:50.720 --> 03:51.960
I don't deserve to be your sister.

03:54.040 --> 03:55.680
Zhao, don't say that.

03:56.360 --> 03:58.000
That was our plan.

03:58.080 --> 04:00.600
Look. I'm all right now.

04:01.680 --> 04:03.160
Don't be sad, Zhao.

04:03.880 --> 04:05.240
My mother said

04:05.320 --> 04:08.480
a handwoven longevity thread
embodied sincerity.

04:08.560 --> 04:11.120
Every knot would bind good luck.

04:11.200 --> 04:13.640
You made this for me by yourself.

04:13.720 --> 04:14.680
I'm quite happy.

04:17.320 --> 04:20.440
What do you think
if I pair it with a jade pendant?

04:21.040 --> 04:22.079
Or a gold lock.

04:22.600 --> 04:23.720
It would look more regal.

04:28.040 --> 04:29.160
I'm sorry.

04:30.280 --> 04:31.160
I'm truly sorry.

04:35.440 --> 04:37.040
Don't say sorry to me.

04:37.120 --> 04:39.920
We came up with the plan together
to catch the villain.

04:40.640 --> 04:42.640
Sadly, it turned out to be Uncle Xun.

04:42.720 --> 04:44.520
But I protected you.

04:45.080 --> 04:46.080
I'm really happy about that.

05:00.040 --> 05:01.920
Uncle, what food have you brought?

05:11.720 --> 05:12.560
Feed me.

05:18.440 --> 05:19.520
What a hassle.

05:28.840 --> 05:29.760
You're not feeding a horse.

05:29.840 --> 05:31.520
It's how soldiers feed people.

05:31.600 --> 05:32.880
You're getting back at me.

05:32.960 --> 05:34.080
You're slandering me.

05:36.920 --> 05:38.000
I won't bring you food anymore.

05:48.680 --> 05:49.760
Aren't you on duty?

05:49.840 --> 05:52.960
How do you have time to bring food to Yu?

05:59.040 --> 06:00.440
My cloak. Return it.

06:03.760 --> 06:05.080
You don't like it, do you?

06:06.280 --> 06:07.680
Why do you want it back now?

06:08.240 --> 06:10.480
I intended to give it to someone else.

06:25.720 --> 06:27.080
I lent that to you.

06:27.680 --> 06:28.800
After you use it,

06:29.480 --> 06:30.520
you give it back.

07:02.400 --> 07:03.240
Take it then.

07:09.640 --> 07:11.640
Uncle, what are you snatching?

07:11.720 --> 07:12.680
I wasn't snatching.

07:13.400 --> 07:15.120
I got back my own cloak.

07:18.520 --> 07:21.440
Zhao, do you remember your promise?

07:31.000 --> 07:32.480
Pretty, huh?

07:32.560 --> 07:33.640
Like falling petals.

07:34.680 --> 07:35.720
Here. Blow again.

07:36.760 --> 07:39.120
You promised him this.
Why do I have to do it?

07:42.520 --> 07:44.000
I order you to do this for me.

08:02.520 --> 08:03.960
Is this swing sturdy enough?

08:04.560 --> 08:05.920
It can hold both of us, right?

08:06.000 --> 08:07.760
I won't play on this with you.

08:07.840 --> 08:09.480
Why?

08:09.560 --> 08:11.120
Swinging is so much fun.

08:11.640 --> 08:12.960
It lets us see distant views.

08:13.040 --> 08:14.480
Oh, boy.

08:14.560 --> 08:16.120
You can go outside and see the views.

08:16.800 --> 08:18.400
Why must you ride a swing?

08:19.880 --> 08:21.040
Can I really go outside?

08:29.680 --> 08:30.520
Come over.

08:31.280 --> 08:33.320
Falling petals!

08:43.559 --> 08:44.560
If you tie like this,

08:44.640 --> 08:45.960
when you finish,

08:46.560 --> 08:48.480
you'll sit on it and fall.

08:48.560 --> 08:50.360
I'm making a tight knot.

08:50.880 --> 08:51.760
How could we fall?

08:52.440 --> 08:53.480
You can fall.

08:54.520 --> 08:55.600
But if he falls,

08:56.280 --> 08:57.120
it would be big trouble.

08:58.480 --> 08:59.880
Don't underestimate me.

09:25.800 --> 09:27.360
Your Highness, you just

09:28.240 --> 09:30.760
wouldn't believe me until you fell.

09:33.640 --> 09:34.480
How did this happen?

09:35.760 --> 09:37.360
I'm sure I tied a tight knot.

09:40.200 --> 09:42.920
Zhao, do you really know
how to make a swing?

09:49.800 --> 09:52.080
We soldiers use this knot
to tie up prisoners.

09:52.680 --> 09:53.920
Once tied,

09:54.440 --> 09:56.600
no one can break free, whoever he is.

10:03.040 --> 10:04.720
-Come on.
-I dare not.

10:06.320 --> 10:07.160
You do it, Zhao.

10:56.600 --> 10:57.720
Zhao.

10:59.200 --> 11:03.280
Let Uncle Xun go back to Xiaonan.

11:04.280 --> 11:06.520
Yu, what did you say?

11:07.240 --> 11:10.040
Stop fighting him.

11:17.920 --> 11:19.200
He's right.

11:19.800 --> 11:21.240
The Lord of Xiaonan still holds power.

11:22.320 --> 11:23.760
Xiao Xun is hard to deal with.

11:24.360 --> 11:25.800
If he remains in the Capital

11:26.320 --> 11:27.360
and fights you,

11:28.040 --> 11:29.280
you'll both suffer.

11:29.360 --> 11:31.280
This time, he escaped by luck.

11:31.880 --> 11:33.040
Next time, he won't.

11:33.920 --> 11:35.640
I know Xiao Xun has wild ambitions.

11:37.320 --> 11:38.800
But what on earth did he do

11:39.400 --> 11:40.640
that made you hate him?

11:41.200 --> 11:43.000
He went in person to Yunzhong to propose.

11:43.080 --> 11:44.200
I thought he cared

11:44.720 --> 11:45.560
about you.

11:49.320 --> 11:50.560
You…

11:51.280 --> 11:52.840
You loved each other, didn't you?

11:54.440 --> 11:55.760
Loved each other?

11:58.800 --> 12:00.920
That's the stupidest thing I've ever done.

12:02.200 --> 12:03.640
Even thinking of it

12:04.520 --> 12:06.000
makes me sick now.

12:14.480 --> 12:15.680
What have you been through?

12:27.800 --> 12:28.720
Jiu,

12:30.360 --> 12:31.640
do you believe

12:33.160 --> 12:35.040
one can live a second life?

12:39.520 --> 12:41.320
<i>In my past life,</i>

12:42.840 --> 12:44.680
<i>I married Xiao Xun as I wished</i>

12:45.600 --> 12:46.760
<i>and became the Empress.</i>

12:46.840 --> 12:47.680
TAIJI HALL

12:49.240 --> 12:51.240
<i>Yet because of this,</i>
<i>I got my father killed.</i>

12:51.880 --> 12:53.280
<i>So was my entire clan.</i>

12:54.720 --> 12:57.680
<i>I was also strangled by Xiao Xun.</i>

13:05.960 --> 13:07.600
You think that's funny, don't you?

13:10.400 --> 13:13.240
Just pretend it was a dream I had.

13:14.960 --> 13:16.040
No.

13:22.560 --> 13:23.840
Everything

13:24.920 --> 13:26.360
exists for a reason.

13:28.520 --> 13:29.360
My father told me

13:30.280 --> 13:33.000
that people must bear
the consequences of their choices.

13:34.800 --> 13:35.680
Just no regrets.

13:40.440 --> 13:41.360
But this time,

13:43.360 --> 13:44.840
you laid a trap for Xiao Xun.

13:46.080 --> 13:47.360
He suffered a quiet defeat.

13:48.600 --> 13:49.920
Once he's on guard,

13:50.440 --> 13:53.000
killing him won't be easy.

13:55.760 --> 13:59.120
He escaped by luck once.

14:01.040 --> 14:02.160
I won't give him another chance.

14:05.640 --> 14:06.720
Then, do you have a plan?

14:10.840 --> 14:13.640
If I do, will you help me?

14:34.160 --> 14:36.000
-Hit him!
-Hit him!

14:36.080 --> 14:40.800
Hit him!

14:40.880 --> 14:44.080
Hit him!

14:51.960 --> 14:56.080
CAPITAL

15:14.800 --> 15:15.920
<i>If I do,</i>

15:16.520 --> 15:17.560
<i>will you help me?</i>

15:22.120 --> 15:23.040
I will.

15:33.320 --> 15:36.760
The temple rite incident has concluded.

15:36.840 --> 15:38.560
The accused were executed.

15:38.640 --> 15:41.320
The imperial city
has been thoroughly purged.

15:41.920 --> 15:46.560
Everyone should learn from this
and never make mistakes.

15:49.200 --> 15:50.040
Oh.

15:50.120 --> 15:51.640
I've been thinking.

15:52.240 --> 15:54.840
Uncle Xun has been
a hostage for seven years.

15:54.920 --> 15:55.960
How pitiful.

15:57.040 --> 15:59.720
Shall we let him go back to Xiaonan?

16:00.600 --> 16:02.680
What do you think?

16:02.760 --> 16:04.240
Absolutely not.

16:06.520 --> 16:08.520
Your Majesty, this is inappropriate.

16:09.120 --> 16:11.840
I'm sure all the ministers have doubts.

16:11.920 --> 16:15.560
Mr. Xie, you claimed
that His Majesty was wise.

16:15.640 --> 16:18.440
But now you're questioning
His Majesty's decision.

16:18.520 --> 16:20.240
That's not right, Mr. Deng.

16:20.920 --> 16:22.360
I've thought about it.

16:23.040 --> 16:24.640
Keeping Mr. Xiao as a hostage

16:24.720 --> 16:26.360
was the late emperor's last wish.

16:26.440 --> 16:28.960
And keeping him in the Capital

16:29.040 --> 16:30.720
can restrain his father.

16:30.800 --> 16:32.440
If we let him go,

16:32.960 --> 16:34.200
changes may occur.

16:34.880 --> 16:36.800
It makes sense, Mr. Xie.

16:36.880 --> 16:39.840
But Xiao Xun has endured a lot here.

16:39.920 --> 16:42.600
If any of that displeases his father,

16:42.680 --> 16:45.560
it'll threaten the court's stability.

16:52.960 --> 16:55.840
Your Highness, what do you think?

16:56.760 --> 16:59.160
Am I entitled to participate in this?

16:59.240 --> 17:00.600
By the late emperor's edict,

17:01.200 --> 17:03.600
the Grand Princess and Grand Mentor
oversee the court.

17:04.319 --> 17:05.520
So you are entitled.

17:06.680 --> 17:07.560
Your Majesty

17:07.640 --> 17:09.200
and ministers,

17:10.000 --> 17:11.720
I've received

17:11.800 --> 17:13.720
a secret report about the Northern Desert.

17:17.520 --> 17:19.040
I didn't mean to stir up trouble,

17:19.119 --> 17:22.359
but since Mr. Xie asked, I will be frank.

17:23.960 --> 17:26.680
Unusual movements have frequently
occurred on the frontier.

17:26.760 --> 17:28.440
Enemy troops seem to be massing.

17:29.400 --> 17:30.800
In the Capital,

17:30.880 --> 17:33.480
suspicious incidents have also occurred.

17:34.080 --> 17:36.640
Everywhere, unidentified figures
are roaming.

17:36.720 --> 17:39.160
They gather in secret
and behave suspiciously.

17:43.440 --> 17:44.480
Your Highness,

17:45.280 --> 17:47.400
can I read this report?

17:47.480 --> 17:48.600
No.

17:50.040 --> 17:51.960
This is a serious matter.

17:52.040 --> 17:55.440
I need to verify
the authenticity of this report

17:55.520 --> 17:56.880
or innocent people may be involved.

17:56.960 --> 17:58.920
If this report is true,

17:59.440 --> 18:00.720
what should we do?

18:01.720 --> 18:03.360
Then the heir to the Lord of Xiaonan

18:03.880 --> 18:05.400
must not leave the Capital.

18:07.120 --> 18:09.360
Xiaonan Prefecture is adjacent
to the Northern Desert.

18:09.960 --> 18:11.720
If they collude with each other…

18:13.720 --> 18:14.960
The Lord of Xiaonan didn't come

18:15.040 --> 18:17.800
to His Majesty's coronation.

18:18.440 --> 18:21.640
It's hard to say
if he's been disloyal all along.

18:30.360 --> 18:32.680
TWO HOURS AGO

18:33.360 --> 18:34.520
Your Highness,

18:34.600 --> 18:37.000
the Pine Soot Ink
is exclusive to the Xie Family.

18:37.080 --> 18:39.560
You deliberately used it in this report.

18:39.640 --> 18:41.520
What if the Xie Family

18:42.040 --> 18:43.240
finds out?

18:43.840 --> 18:45.200
That's exactly what I want.

18:46.640 --> 18:49.560
If we release Xiao Xun,
we'll be releasing an enemy.

18:50.080 --> 18:51.880
We'll lose all control over Xiaonan.

18:51.960 --> 18:54.200
Once trouble arises,
Gaoyang will be affected.

18:54.280 --> 18:56.480
Xie Yanfang is the head of his clan.

18:56.560 --> 18:58.360
He wouldn't allow this to happen.

18:58.440 --> 19:01.160
Therefore, he'll prevent it.

19:02.280 --> 19:04.160
With the Pine Soot Ink from his clan,

19:06.320 --> 19:07.480
in this matter,

19:08.200 --> 19:11.200
he's fully bound to me.

19:11.800 --> 19:13.400
I don't quite understand.

19:13.920 --> 19:16.800
Why is Mr. Deng so eager
to have Mr. Xiao leave?

19:17.400 --> 19:18.600
Isn't he supposed

19:19.240 --> 19:21.280
to speak in your favor?

19:22.920 --> 19:24.560
Court struggles have been like this.

19:25.760 --> 19:27.480
No permanent enemies.

19:27.560 --> 19:29.120
No permanent allies.

19:29.640 --> 19:32.320
That's why I must drag the Xie Family in.

19:34.280 --> 19:37.360
Because only an accomplice
will desperately keep a secret.

19:38.160 --> 19:39.560
Even if this secret report

19:40.240 --> 19:41.560
turns out to be false,

19:42.840 --> 19:44.360
it has to be true.

20:21.120 --> 20:23.440
I haven't mastered this move.

20:24.120 --> 20:25.440
I'll practice more.

20:28.280 --> 20:30.240
Living inside the palace,

20:31.480 --> 20:33.400
you got news bout the Northern Desert.

20:34.560 --> 20:37.560
You really have
good sources of information.

20:37.640 --> 20:39.640
You weren't in the court,

20:40.160 --> 20:42.520
but knew what happened there.

20:43.200 --> 20:44.560
You're actually well-informed.

20:56.280 --> 20:57.640
You want to drag the Xie Family in.

20:59.480 --> 21:01.400
Do you know how dangerous

21:01.480 --> 21:02.360
it could be?

21:06.720 --> 21:07.560
Chu Zhao,

21:08.880 --> 21:11.200
no one can play petty tricks
under Xie Yanfang's nose.

21:12.680 --> 21:13.520
You're no exception.

21:14.320 --> 21:15.880
I want to be an exception.

21:18.720 --> 21:21.200
If he exposes
that you forged the secret report

21:22.280 --> 21:23.480
and framed the Xie Family,

21:25.000 --> 21:26.440
what will you do?

21:27.040 --> 21:29.280
Still wait until the young kid
saves you again?

21:29.360 --> 21:31.160
Then I'll say

21:32.560 --> 21:33.600
you gave me that ink.

21:34.880 --> 21:36.400
Let's see if Xie Yanfang

21:37.160 --> 21:38.800
will abandon his brother.

21:45.840 --> 21:47.720
No one can read his mind.

21:47.800 --> 21:48.920
Jiu,

21:50.880 --> 21:52.040
you will help me,

21:52.680 --> 21:53.720
right?

21:56.600 --> 21:58.440
You fought on the frontier for years.

21:59.080 --> 22:02.320
You must know
the looks and dressing habits

22:02.400 --> 22:03.560
of Northern Desert soldiers.

22:05.480 --> 22:06.320
Can you tell me?

22:07.760 --> 22:08.680
So,

22:09.800 --> 22:11.040
you've had a plan.

22:12.800 --> 22:15.080
What a perfect bait.

22:15.600 --> 22:17.040
She faked a secret report

22:17.120 --> 22:18.640
to confine Xiao Xun in the Capital.

22:18.720 --> 22:20.480
Xiao Xun is so suspicious

22:20.560 --> 22:22.600
that he'll take this for a trap.

22:23.200 --> 22:25.000
Then he'll speed up his escape plan.

22:25.680 --> 22:28.120
The spies I sent out told me

22:28.800 --> 22:30.040
Chu Zhao arranged some men

22:30.120 --> 22:32.600
to secretly bury weapons
along the way to Xiaonan.

22:32.680 --> 22:34.680
When Xiao Xun reaches the border area,

22:35.640 --> 22:37.840
fake Northern Desert soldiers
will get him.

22:38.360 --> 22:39.880
Once Xiao Xun escapes,

22:39.960 --> 22:41.920
he'll be shot dead immediately

22:42.000 --> 22:43.880
in the name of collusion
and armed treason.

22:45.280 --> 22:46.120
Grand Mentor,

22:47.200 --> 22:48.640
once Xiao Xun dies,

22:49.280 --> 22:50.560
you'll have no way out.

22:58.720 --> 23:00.400
I have my own plans.

23:02.400 --> 23:04.320
If Xiao Xun escapes the Capital,

23:04.840 --> 23:08.200
I'll have rumors spread
that the heir to the Lord of Xiaonan

23:08.720 --> 23:10.080
led Northern Desert soldiers in.

23:11.280 --> 23:12.920
He'll be seen as a traitor

23:14.120 --> 23:15.240
and killed on sight.

23:16.600 --> 23:19.040
-If no obstacles arise…
-No obstacles.

23:20.200 --> 23:21.160
If there are,

23:22.240 --> 23:23.280
I'll destroy them.

23:25.240 --> 23:29.440
<i>A forgery woven from truth</i>
<i>is the hardest to disprove.</i>

23:29.520 --> 23:32.680
<i>As someone reborn, I know it better</i>
<i>than anyone else.</i>

23:32.760 --> 23:36.680
<i>The Lord of Xiaonan and his heir</i>
<i>do collude with Northern Desert foes.</i>

23:41.920 --> 23:42.760
Your Highness.

23:44.320 --> 23:45.240
Any news?

23:46.000 --> 23:47.000
Chu Zhao did receive a report

23:47.080 --> 23:49.920
about you and your father
raising troops and colluding with foes.

23:52.840 --> 23:55.240
How does she know all these things?

23:56.040 --> 23:57.160
Over the past years,

23:57.760 --> 23:59.240
I've stayed vigilant!

23:59.880 --> 24:02.480
There's no way she could know
about the collusion thing.

24:03.240 --> 24:04.480
This woman is cunning.

24:04.560 --> 24:07.560
She must blind you with a pretense
and let down your guard.

24:10.880 --> 24:11.920
No way.

24:14.640 --> 24:15.840
If I stay here,

24:17.440 --> 24:19.600
they can execute me

24:20.400 --> 24:23.120
in public with that secret report.

24:24.560 --> 24:25.480
But if I flee,

24:26.280 --> 24:28.200
I'll be convicted of treason

24:29.200 --> 24:30.280
and get killed there.

24:30.360 --> 24:33.200
Whatever choice we make,

24:34.000 --> 24:34.960
she will

24:35.560 --> 24:37.840
firmly hold the initiative.

24:38.440 --> 24:41.320
After years of planning,
will we fall like this?

24:42.240 --> 24:44.840
That day in the court,
we actually had the upper hand.

24:45.440 --> 24:46.800
How did things turn out like this?

24:47.320 --> 24:48.600
What exactly went wrong?

24:49.960 --> 24:51.440
What's gone is gone.

24:52.360 --> 24:53.520
Don't bring it up.

24:54.280 --> 24:55.240
But now,

24:56.320 --> 24:57.440
maybe we have

24:58.280 --> 25:00.440
a third option.

25:02.400 --> 25:03.960
Still haven't found her?

25:04.040 --> 25:06.560
Forgive us. We sent three teams on it.

25:06.640 --> 25:08.600
We found her. We did.

25:08.680 --> 25:10.240
Old Madam is back.

25:10.320 --> 25:12.360
The Grand Princess sent her back.

25:22.120 --> 25:23.280
Your Highness, my mother--

25:23.360 --> 25:25.120
She has been sent back to rest.

25:29.440 --> 25:32.200
I met your mother at the corner
of the West Market.

25:33.280 --> 25:34.200
As I caught sight of her,

25:35.240 --> 25:36.840
she was picking up vegetable leaves

25:37.360 --> 25:38.400
from the ground.

25:43.080 --> 25:44.600
Born in the countryside,

25:45.120 --> 25:45.960
she's been frugal.

25:51.720 --> 25:55.600
Only those who starved
would treasure every grain.

25:56.520 --> 25:58.760
Just like people all desire wealth.

25:59.840 --> 26:01.480
This is human nature.

26:08.040 --> 26:09.400
It's her personal preference.

26:09.920 --> 26:11.080
Please don't mock her.

26:12.160 --> 26:13.680
Why would I mock her?

26:15.320 --> 26:16.920
You truly have talent

26:17.000 --> 26:19.080
to rise to the Grand Mentor

26:19.760 --> 26:21.960
from a country boy.

26:22.480 --> 26:23.760
Your hard work

26:23.840 --> 26:25.880
is far beyond what others can imagine.

26:26.480 --> 26:27.720
Such diligence

26:28.880 --> 26:30.880
should be admirable.

26:36.040 --> 26:38.120
This is the braided longevity thread.

26:39.240 --> 26:40.560
Each knot

26:41.360 --> 26:42.760
can bind good luck.

26:43.680 --> 26:45.440
You didn't come here so late

26:46.080 --> 26:48.760
just to give me this, did you?

26:49.920 --> 26:52.720
I wonder if I can trade so much good luck

26:53.520 --> 26:55.080
for something from you.

26:56.840 --> 26:57.680
What is it?

26:58.360 --> 26:59.600
Xiao Xun's life.

27:07.920 --> 27:09.600
Are you so confident

27:09.680 --> 27:11.040
that you can kill him?

27:11.760 --> 27:12.600
Yes.

27:14.080 --> 27:15.360
So, Mr. Deng,

27:16.920 --> 27:18.560
please stay out of this.

27:22.520 --> 27:23.680
Once Xiao Xun dies,

27:24.400 --> 27:25.840
his treasures and forces

27:25.920 --> 27:28.080
he has gathered in the Capital
all these years

27:29.360 --> 27:30.360
will be yours.

27:34.640 --> 27:37.880
Your Highness doesn't blame me
for opposing you in court?

27:37.960 --> 27:38.840
I do.

27:39.440 --> 27:41.640
If you ruin my plan,

27:42.560 --> 27:43.840
I'll use these treasures

27:44.920 --> 27:46.640
to have you killed.

27:55.360 --> 27:56.600
Just kidding.

27:57.200 --> 27:58.440
Don't worry, Mr. Deng.

28:02.000 --> 28:06.000
So, you haven't told me your answer.

28:10.440 --> 28:11.760
It's easy to have wealth.

28:14.200 --> 28:16.000
But it's hard to have confidants.

28:18.840 --> 28:20.040
Deal.

28:20.760 --> 28:22.600
I always keep my word.

28:23.360 --> 28:24.680
So, Mr. Deng,

28:25.320 --> 28:26.440
hope you won't go back on yours.

28:29.480 --> 28:30.920
I won't.

28:35.640 --> 28:36.480
‎Your Highness,

28:36.560 --> 28:39.920
‎Mr. Xie is here on His Majesty's order.
‎He's been waiting for long.

28:55.480 --> 28:56.360
Waiting for me?

29:02.560 --> 29:03.600
I'm just

29:05.480 --> 29:07.120
enjoying the moon.

29:09.920 --> 29:11.040
You're really in the mood.

29:11.720 --> 29:14.480
You enjoy the moon
right in front of my palace.

29:16.720 --> 29:19.720
Were you worrying about me
during my visit to Deng Yi's place?

29:20.560 --> 29:22.000
So, you've been waiting for me.

29:23.200 --> 29:24.560
In front of your Qiwu Palace,

29:25.520 --> 29:26.880
the moonlight is rather bleak.

29:29.280 --> 29:31.160
Bleak moonlight over a lonely minister.

29:31.680 --> 29:32.720
Perfect.

29:37.040 --> 29:38.920
I'm only here by the order of His Majesty.

29:43.800 --> 29:45.160
I've been informed

29:45.960 --> 29:47.520
that Xiao Xun will leave tomorrow.

29:48.200 --> 29:49.240
How confident are you

29:49.760 --> 29:51.640
he'll take the official road
as you planned?

29:52.320 --> 29:53.960
Tomorrow, I'll send naval forces

29:54.040 --> 29:55.680
to block all merchant ships

29:55.760 --> 29:57.240
in the name of inspecting smuggled salt.

29:58.720 --> 30:00.240
Once the dock is cut off,

30:01.000 --> 30:03.760
Xiao Xun will have to take
the official road.

30:22.480 --> 30:23.880
In that case,

30:25.280 --> 30:28.240
I've arranged crossbowmen at Woniu Ridge.

30:29.240 --> 30:31.880
Once Xiao Xun leaves the Capital,

30:33.080 --> 30:36.200
he'll be shot to death right there.

30:42.680 --> 30:46.120
Nothing shall go wrong tomorrow.

30:51.120 --> 30:52.040
Rest assured.

30:54.680 --> 30:56.360
Tomorrow, I'll lead the ambush myself.

30:59.280 --> 31:00.520
Nothing will go wrong.

31:03.040 --> 31:06.000
‎WATERWAY OF THE STATE OF CHU

31:10.960 --> 31:12.160
Oh, Zhao.

31:13.040 --> 31:15.240
I don't know why you do this to me.

31:16.840 --> 31:18.040
But anyway,

31:19.160 --> 31:21.520
you've failed to trap me.

31:22.800 --> 31:23.640
Your Highness.

31:23.720 --> 31:24.680
Your Highness.

31:26.000 --> 31:27.440
Xiao Xun ran off with his men.

31:27.520 --> 31:29.400
-By the official road?
-No.

31:29.480 --> 31:30.760
What?

31:31.480 --> 31:33.440
The whole dock is blocked by naval forces.

31:33.520 --> 31:36.160
To leave the Capital,
that is his only option. How come?

31:36.240 --> 31:38.640
No trace of them
was found on the official road.

31:38.720 --> 31:39.640
But our spies reported

31:39.720 --> 31:42.640
that a merchant ship sailed earlier
at the third quarter of the Yin hour.

31:46.240 --> 31:47.320
We've been tricked.

31:49.280 --> 31:50.320
He escaped again.

31:50.400 --> 31:52.200
Mr. Xie already led his men
to go after them.

32:15.400 --> 32:16.360
Xie Yanlai.

32:17.200 --> 32:18.360
I promised Her Highness

32:19.440 --> 32:20.680
that you wouldn't live.

32:21.360 --> 32:24.120
Are you sure Zhao wants me dead?

32:25.000 --> 32:26.560
She loved me so much.

32:27.160 --> 32:28.080
That was before.

32:30.640 --> 32:31.520
Now,

32:32.600 --> 32:33.800
she wants you dead.

32:34.680 --> 32:36.080
I forgot to ask you.

32:37.200 --> 32:38.040
The boy of the Wei Village

32:39.000 --> 32:40.680
who survived alone…

32:41.360 --> 32:42.320
Xiang.

32:42.920 --> 32:44.080
Did he take revenge on you?

32:49.320 --> 32:51.480
<i>I'm Xiang. What's your name?</i>

33:44.160 --> 33:45.040
<i>Xiang,</i>

33:46.600 --> 33:47.640
<i>where are you?</i>

33:49.800 --> 33:51.000
<i>It was all my fault.</i>

34:18.679 --> 34:20.000
Mr. Xie is seriously injured.

34:20.600 --> 34:22.320
Thankfully, he was treated in time.

34:22.400 --> 34:24.880
I've bandaged his wound.

34:24.960 --> 34:28.199
I'll go make a prescription
to bring down his fever.

34:28.880 --> 34:30.880
He lost too much blood.

34:30.960 --> 34:33.320
He must rest very well to recover.

34:47.840 --> 34:50.560
Your Highness, we got a tip.

34:51.280 --> 34:54.600
Xiao Xun has fled to Xiaonan.

34:59.760 --> 35:01.320
It will be even harder

35:02.160 --> 35:03.000
to kill him.

35:22.040 --> 35:23.800
I thought my plan was flawless.

35:25.280 --> 35:27.240
Yet I was one move short.

35:28.680 --> 35:30.320
Sorry to have dragged you into this.

35:33.480 --> 35:34.960
You used to say you owed me.

35:36.280 --> 35:37.280
Now,

35:39.920 --> 35:41.600
I owe you.

35:56.280 --> 35:57.560
Zhao.

36:08.240 --> 36:09.080
Your Highness.

36:27.360 --> 36:29.760
Have you found the man I asked for?

36:30.640 --> 36:32.320
It's Fang Du, a follower of Deng Yi.

36:33.440 --> 36:35.480
Last year, he became a Naval Commander.

36:35.560 --> 36:38.160
Xiao Xun's ship managed to leave the dock

36:38.240 --> 36:39.240
with his pass.

36:47.440 --> 36:49.920
What a duplicitous Deng Yi.

37:18.200 --> 37:19.960
Your Highness, why did you break in here

37:20.480 --> 37:21.760
so late at night?

37:24.720 --> 37:26.000
Mr. Deng,

37:26.520 --> 37:28.920
I'm here to give you a present.

37:29.760 --> 37:31.200
I've heard you like rare wood.

37:31.280 --> 37:33.280
The golden-thread nanmu

37:33.360 --> 37:34.920
is of noble grade.

37:35.760 --> 37:38.640
I wonder if you like it.

37:39.240 --> 37:40.760
No merit, no reward.

37:41.280 --> 37:42.360
I'm not worthy

37:43.960 --> 37:45.320
of this present.

37:46.160 --> 37:47.920
How could you not be worthy?

37:50.360 --> 37:51.360
You asked Fang Du

37:52.240 --> 37:53.920
to give that permission.

37:55.480 --> 37:57.680
You "helped" me really much.

37:58.360 --> 38:01.760
How could I not reward you?

38:03.880 --> 38:06.320
Buried underground,
this wood will never rot.

38:07.280 --> 38:10.600
It's a perfect fit for your great merit.

38:12.560 --> 38:13.840
You must be kidding.

38:13.920 --> 38:15.360
Kidding?

38:16.200 --> 38:19.720
I'm being really serious
to give you this reward.

38:21.640 --> 38:22.480
What?

38:23.000 --> 38:24.280
You don't like it?

38:24.920 --> 38:26.960
Or will you defy my order?

38:32.440 --> 38:33.360
I like it.

38:33.440 --> 38:36.760
In that case, keep it very well.

38:37.440 --> 38:40.240
Put it in the yard,
so you can look at it every day.

38:40.320 --> 38:42.600
Without my order, it mustn't be removed.

38:46.760 --> 38:47.720
Your Highness,

38:48.480 --> 38:50.440
thank you for your reward.

38:51.040 --> 38:52.440
You're welcome, Mr. Deng.

38:53.000 --> 38:54.360
After all…

38:57.120 --> 38:58.240
we have a long way to go.

39:02.520 --> 39:05.240
If you think
the longevity thread is too long,

39:05.320 --> 39:06.800
I can give you a shorter one.
